name: PotentiallyHarmfulAntipsychoticsForOlderAdults
title: Potentially Harmful Antipsychotics for Older Adults
purpose: (Clinical Focus: The purpose of this value set is to represent concepts for potentially harmful antipsychotics for older adults as described in the 2023 American Geriatrics Society BEERS criteria.),(Data Element Scope: This value set may use a model element related to Medication.),(Inclusion Criteria: Includes concepts that represent generic, human use and prescribable antipsychotic medications.),(Exclusion Criteria: Excludes concepts that represent non-prescribable or branded drugs and excludes concepts that represent components or ingredients.)
